OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779696396
OL,3,CBolton Wanderers secure promotion to
OL,4,CChampionship
OL,6,FBolton Wanderers are back in the
OL,7,FChampionship for the first time since
OL,8,F2019 after a 4-1 League One play-off
OL,9,Ffinal win over Stockport County.
OL,11,FSubstitute Sam Dalby came off the
OL,12,Fbench and netted a decisive 81st-
OL,13,Fminute third goal after playing his
OL,14,Fpart in Wanderers' restoring their
OL,15,Flead via a Kyle Wootton own goal 17
OL,16,Fminutes earlier.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
