PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779696396
OL,3,CBolton Wanderers secure promotion to
OL,4,CChampionship
OL,6,FRuben Rodrigues started and finished
OL,7,Fthe scoring as County's second Wembley
OL,8,Fdefeat of the season ended with former
OL,9,FBolton right-back Josh Dacres-Cogley
OL,10,Fsent-off for a stoppage-time hair pull
OL,11,Fon Ibrahim Cissoko.
OL,13,FSteven Schumacher's side celebrated
OL,14,Ftheir return to the second tier two
OL,15,Fyears after losing to Oxford in the
OL,16,Fsame showpiece.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779696396
OL,3,CBolton Wanderers secure promotion to
OL,4,CChampionship
OL,6,FRodrigues gave Bolton a third-minute
OL,7,Flead, but after seeing a potential
OL,8,Fequaliser ruled out by a controversial
OL,9,FVAR decision Adama Sidibeh headed a
OL,10,F29th-minute leveller for the Hatters.
OL,12,FWith the temperature exceeding 30
OL,13,Fdegrees, Bolton turned up the heat
OL,14,Fthemselves, forcing Wootton to turn
OL,15,Fthe ball into his own net.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779696396
OL,3,CBolton Wanderers secure promotion to
OL,4,CChampionship
OL,6,FHot shot striker Dalby's brilliant
OL,7,Foverhead kick for his 14th goal of the
OL,8,Fseason and Rodrigues' second after
OL,9,FDacres-Cogley's dismissal started wild
OL,10,Fcelebrations among Bolton's near
OL,11,F30,000 fans.
OL,13,FRodrigues gave Bolton a dream start
OL,14,Fbut for goalkeeper Corey Addai it was
OL,15,Fa nightmare first involvement.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779696396
OL,3,CBolton Wanderers secure promotion to
OL,4,CChampionship
OL,6,FThierry Gale's 30-yarder was on target
OL,7,Fbut lacked power. Addai, though,
OL,8,Fneedlessly scooped the ball into Mason
OL,9,FBurstow's path before Ethan Pye
OL,10,Fcleared the Hull loanee's attempt
OL,11,Fstraight to Rodrigues who fired home.
OL,13,FEight minutes later, the Hatters
OL,14,Fthought they had levelled through
OL,15,FSidibeh's 10th goal since his January
OL,16,Fswitch from St Johnstone. Instead, a
OL,17,FVAR intervention decided otherwise and
OL,18,Freferee Josh Smith overturned his on-
OL,19,Fpitch call to award a free-kick to
OL,20,FWanderers for a "careless foul" on
OL,21,Fdefender George Johnston.
OL,26,@|D@QOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779696396
OL,3,CBolton Wanderers secure promotion to
OL,4,CChampionship
OL,6,FAfter the game's first drinks break,
OL,7,FSidibeh did take his tally into double
OL,8,Ffigures. Odin Bailey teased a cross
OL,9,Ffrom the Wanderers' left into the six-
OL,10,Fyard box and the unmarked Gambia
OL,11,Fstriker headed home.
OL,13,FAddai saved unconvincingly again, this
OL,14,Ftime from Josh Sheehan, at the start
OL,15,Fof the second period while Rodrigues
OL,16,Fcould not convert with a curling shot
OL,17,Fafter Gale's tenacity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779696396
OL,3,CBolton Wanderers secure promotion to
OL,4,CChampionship
OL,6,FDalby replaced Xavier Simons on the
OL,7,Fhour and three minutes later the
OL,8,Fsubstitute made his first telling
OL,9,Fcontribution. His pass sent in Amario
OL,10,FCozier-Duberry but Addai could only
OL,11,Fpush the winger's weak effort on to
OL,12,FWootton who unwittingly deflected it
OL,13,Finto his own net.
OL,15,FOpposite number Jack Bonham then
OL,16,Fshowed his worth, blocking substitute
OL,17,FTanto Olaofe's goal bound strike. It
OL,18,Fproved a crucial intervention as Dalby
OL,19,Fand Portuguese star Rodrigues ensured
OL,20,FBolton's seventh play-off final
OL,21,Fappearance ended in glory.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
